description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 2, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 2, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 2 for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90021-42162-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [2 Votes, Common]
